title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Canis Castigator SUV
content:
The Canis Castigator rides a very thin line: it’s the only SUV in the world with a net-negative carbon footprint that’s also capable of grinding the most remote wilderness trail into a muddy pulp.

Grab a Castigator for yourself from Southern San Andreas Super Autos or scope it out at the Luxury Autos showroom. You can also acquire one for free by completing all the Tier 4 Career Progress Challenges for Bottom Dollar Bounties.
